The command that sets the parameters of `/deck` command.```
/deck-setting
```will display buttons for setting parameters.

The colored buttons are the selected parameters, and the gray buttons are the **not selected** buttons. By pressing the buttons, you can change the selection or deselection.
If `[Balance]` is selected, a relatively balanced deck is generated. If `[Random]` is selected, a completely random deck is generated.
You can initialize the parameters by pressing `[Reset]`.
Press `[Execute]` to generate a deck. A deck can also be generated by `/deck` command.
